The paper deals with personalized services in supermarket chains, which involves analyzing customer behavior and predicting their future purchases. This falls under the domain of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also involves analyzing and processing large amounts of data, which is a common theme in database systems (cs.DB). The use of annotations and sequences also suggests a focus on information retrieval (cs.IR) and pattern recognition (cs.CE).
